CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg 13 reads: "Night Staff - Left to right: John McCormick, clerk; Samuel Patterson, utility clerk; the late Peter V. Morone, chief clerk; Jerry Powell and Joseph R. Thompson, clerks."
TitMainTitle: Five clerks, John McCormick, Samuel Patterson, Peter V. Morone, Henry Powell, and Joseph R. Thompson, gathered around table examining files in Allegheny County Prothonotary office
